title: Josh Woods’s CV
text:
Experience

Facilitate interactive workshops and personalized sessions, resulting in measurable improvements in student performance and comprehension.

text:

Analyzed and discussed different algorithmic approaches to optimize coding solutions.

The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints – Full-time Missionary; Wisconsin Milwaukee Mission
May 2020 - May 2022

Committed 40+ hours per week to community service and outreach initiatives.
Developed effective communication skills through interactions with diverse cultural and linguistic groups.
Led and trained a team of 8 missionaries, facilitating professional development and goal-setting.
Organized and led weekly community service projects, involving local residents and organizations.
